OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry night in the east with late bright
OL,7,Fspells in the evening, and clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight. Cloudier in the west
OL,9,Fwith a few showers possible. Breezier
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA mainly dry morning with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells. Bright spells
OL,14,Fcontinuing in east through the
OL,15,Fafternoon but showers increasingly
OL,16,Fdeveloping from the west. Windy at
OL,17,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
