OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy on Saturday with heavy
OL,7,Fshowers clearing later in the day. Dry
OL,8,FSunday and Monday with sunny spells,
OL,9,Fbut possibly cloudier towards the
OL,10,Fcoasts. Becoming warmer in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
